These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, february, july
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, italian, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, rugby, sailing
1. the thai is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the italian is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
5. the person who's sport is rugby is not the thai##6
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
7. the brazilian is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in february and the colombian##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in february##2
9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | february   | july      | april   | october  |
| Nationality   | thai    | italian   | brazilian | colombian  |
| Sport         | sailing | badminton | rugby     | ice-hockey |

