.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, gospel, jazz, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indian, mexican, nigerian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester, alhambra, baccarat
1. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
2. the indian is the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the fan of gospel is the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the mexican is the fan of salsa##1
6. the argentine is the montecristo-smoker##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
8. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of jazz##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | blues     | salsa   | jazz      |
| Nationality   | indian    | argentine | mexican | nigerian  |
| Cigar     | ritmeester | montecristo  | baccarat    | alhambra |

