.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, iced-tea, lemonade
4 different games are played: whist, snooker, backgammon, monopoly
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, mouse, rabbit
1. the person drinking cola is not the person playing monopoly##6
2. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the person playing whist##7
3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person playing snooker and the person drinking fanta##7
5. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person playing whist is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | cola | iced-tea | lemonade |
| Game   | monopoly | backgammon  | snooker  | whist    |
| Pet           | rabbit | cat  | horse    | mouse    |

