.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-9::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, blueberry, broccoli, papaya
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, cola, 7up
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, goat, goldfish
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person eating asparagus##7
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
8. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
9. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | blueberry  | broccoli  | asparagus | papaya   |
| Beverage   | tea  | 7up | mirinda     | cola   |
| Pet           | chinchilla | dog       | goat      | goldfish |

